{"desi_lesson":{"title":"Greetings & Introductions","target_language":"Kannada","theme":"Greetings & Introductions","vocabulary":[{"english":"hello","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ಕಾರ","transliteration":"namaskaara","pronunciation":"nuh-muh-skaa-rah"},{"english":"good morning","target_language_script":"ಶುಭೋದಯ","transliteration":"shubhodaya","pronunciation":"shuh-bho-day-yah"},{"english":"good afternoon","target_language_script":"ಉತ್ತರಾಹ್ನ","transliteration":"uttarahna","pronunciation":"ut-tar-ah-nah"},{"english":"good evening","target_language_script":"ಸಾಯಂಕಾಲ","transliteration":"saayangala","pronunciation":"sah-yang-gah-lah"},{"english":"good night","target_language_script":"ಶುಭ ರಾತ್ರಿ","transliteration":"shubha ratri","pronunciation":"shuh-bah rah-tree"},{"english":"how are you?","target_language_script":"ನೀವು ಹೇಗಿದ್ದೀರಿ?","transliteration":"neevu hege iddiri?","pronunciation":"nee-vu hey-ge id-dee-ree?"},{"english":"I am fine, thank you","target_language_script":"ನಾನು ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿದ್ದೇನೆ, ಧನ್ಯವಾದಗಳು","transliteration":"naanu chennaagiddeene, dhanyavaadalu","pronunciation":"nah-noo chen-nah-gi-de-nee, dha-nya-vah-da-lu"},{"english":"thank you","target_language_script":"ಧನ್ಯವಾದಗಳು","transliteration":"dhanyavaadalu","pronunciation":"dha-nya-vah-da-lu"},{"english":"my name is...","target_language_script":"ನನ್ನ ಹೆಸರು...","transliteration":"nanna hesaru...","pronunciation":"nan-na hey-sa-roo..."},{"english":"please","target_language_script":"ದಯವಿಟ್ಟು","transliteration":"dayavittu","pronunciation":"day-a-vit-too"}],"example_sentences":[{"english":"Hello, how are you?","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ಕಾರ, ನೀವು ಹೇಗಿದ್ದೀರಿ?","transliteration":"namaskaara, neevu hege iddiri?","pronunciation":"nuh-muh-skaa-rah, nee-vu hey-ge id-dee-ree?"},{"english":"Good morning! I hope you are well.","target_language_script":"ಶುಭೋದಯ! ನೀವು ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿದ್ದೀರಾ ಎಂದು ನಾನು ಆಶಿಸುತ್ತೇನೆ.","transliteration":"shubhodaya! neevu chennaagiddira endu naanu aashisuttene.","pronunciation":"shuh-bho-day-yah! nee-vu ch